---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---
<ServiceLayout
    title="CRM & Growth Infrastructure – Super Sonic"
    description="CRM systems designed to capture, nurture, and convert every opportunity into revenue."
    canonicalUrl="https://supersonic.media/crm/"
>
    <section class="service-hero">
        <div class="tag">CRM &amp; Growth Infrastructure</div>
        <h1>Structured follow-up. <span class="gold">Predictable growth.</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">CRM systems designed to capture, nurture, and convert opportunities.</p>
        <div class="hero-line"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="overview">
        <div class="overview-inner">
            <div class="overview-text">
                <div class="overview-label">Overview</div>
                <p>Most businesses don&#8217;t have a traffic problem. They have a follow-up problem.</p>
                <p>We implement CRM and growth infrastructure that ensures every inquiry is tracked, every lead is nurtured, and every opportunity is visible.</p>
                <p><strong>Your website brings people in. Your CRM turns them into revenue.</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="overview-principles">
                <div class="principle reveal"><h4>Every lead is tracked</h4><p>No inquiry falls through the cracks &#8212; automated capture and routing from day one.</p></div>
                <div class="principle reveal"><h4>Every touchpoint is intentional</h4><p>Sequenced communication that builds trust and drives action.</p></div>
                <div class="principle reveal"><h4>Every metric is visible</h4><p>Pipeline analytics that show exactly where revenue is coming from.</p></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="deliver">
        <div class="section-tag">What We Deliver</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">The infrastructure behind consistent revenue.</h2>
        <div class="deliver-grid">
            <div class="deliver-card reveal">
                <div class="deliver-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Pipeline Management</h3>
                <p>Clarity across every stage of your sales process.</p>
                <div class="deliver-items"><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Deal tracking</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Stage automation</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Task reminders</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Visibility across your team</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="deliver-card reveal">
                <div class="deliver-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"/><polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Automated Follow-Up</h3>
                <p>Consistent communication without manual effort.</p>
                <div class="deliver-items"><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Email sequences</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>SMS automation</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Appointment reminders</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Re-engagement flows</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="deliver-card reveal">
                <div class="deliver-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Reporting &amp; Insights</h3>
                <p>Know what&#8217;s working &#8212; and what isn&#8217;t.</p>
                <div class="deliver-items"><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Conversion tracking</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Pipeline analytics</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Campaign performance</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Lead source reporting</span></div></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="performance">
        <div class="perf-header">
            <div class="section-tag">Why Infrastructure Matters</div>
            <h2>Built with intent.</h2>
            <p>Without structure, leads go cold and opportunities are lost. With the right system, growth becomes measurable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="perf-grid">
            <div class="perf-item reveal"><div class="perf-icon">&#128233;</div><h3>Timely Communication</h3><p>Automated follow-up ensures no lead goes unanswered.</p></div>
            <div class="perf-item reveal"><div class="perf-icon">&#128200;</div><h3>Clear Sales Process</h3><p>Every stage defined, every action tracked.</p></div>
            <div class="perf-item reveal"><div class="perf-icon">&#128260;</div><h3>Consistent Nurture</h3><p>Re-engagement sequences that bring cold leads back to life.</p></div>
            <div class="perf-item reveal"><div class="perf-icon">&#127919;</div><h3>Measurable Growth</h3><p>Pipeline analytics that show exactly what&#8217;s driving revenue.</p></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ideal">
        <div class="ideal-inner">
            <div class="section-tag">Ideal For</div>
            <h2>Is this the right fit?</h2>
            <div class="ideal-items">
                <div class="ideal-item reveal"><span class="ideal-arrow">&#8594;</span><span>Businesses generating leads but lacking process</span></div>
                <div class="ideal-item reveal"><span class="ideal-arrow">&#8594;</span><span>Sales teams needing visibility into their pipeline</span></div>
                <div class="ideal-item reveal"><span class="ideal-arrow">&#8594;</span><span>Founders tired of spreadsheet chaos</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="service-cta">
        <div class="cta-bg"></div>
        <h2>Ready to bring structure to <span class="gold">your growth?</span></h2>
        <p class="cta-sub">Let&#8217;s implement the system that turns leads into revenue.</p>
        <div class="cta-btn-wrap">
            <a href="/start/" class="btn-primary">Let&#8217;s Build It <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 13L13 3M13 3H5M13 3v8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
        </div>
    </section>
</ServiceLayout>
